OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fwarm evening sunshine across the
OL,7,Fcountry. However, cloud and patchy
OL,8,Fdrizzle will persist across northwest
OL,9,FScotland. Dry overnight with prolonged
OL,10,Fclear periods. Some mist and fog
OL,11,Fpatches developing, mainly in the
OL,12,Fwest. A warm night for many.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FEarly mist and fog soon
OL,15,Fclearing. England, Wales and eastern
OL,16,FScotland experiencing another hot day
OL,17,Fwith hazy sunshine and light winds.
OL,18,FCloudier for Northern Ireland and
OL,19,Fnorthwest Scotland.
